name: Fischl | Genshin Impact | 2in1 LoRA & LoCon
description:
A LoRA Model of Fischl from Genshin Impact.

This LoRA includes two official costumes.

There are two sets of trigger words:

For triggering Dunkelnacht Sakrament(Default Costumes):

fischl (dunkelnacht sakrament) (genshin impact), green eyes, (white pupils:1.2), fischl (genshin impact), asymmetrical sleeves, detached collar, detached sleeves, blonde hair, thighhighs, eyepatch, long hair, two side up, single glove, bow, purple bow, black thighhighs, dress, hair over one eye, single glove, bare shoulders, bodystocking, breasts, bangs, purple bowtie, black gloves, bowtie, single leg pantyhose, hair ribbon, single thighhigh, ribbon, medium breasts

For triggering Ein Immernachtstraum:

fischl (ein immernachtstraum) (genshin impact), red eyes, (white pupils:1.2), alternate eye color, fischl (genshin impact), detached collar, detached sleeves, official alternate costume, blonde hair, hair over one eye, tiara, dress, long hair, thighhighs, bare shoulders, white thighhighs, long sleeves, frills, ring, purple dress, puffy sleeves, pantyhose, bangs, white pantyhose, single leg pantyhose, juliet sleeves, breasts, ribbon, frilled sleeves, single thighhigh, jewelry, medium breasts

bonus: For trigger Any Custom Outfit:(experimental)

fischl (genshin impact), green eyes, blonde hair, two side up, eyepatch, long hair, hair over one eye, [Explain in detail what clouthes you would like to trigger......]

Recommend 0.8-1 Strength for triggering any official costume.

For changing custom clothes, I suggest 0.7-0.8 Weight

The preview images were generated by the AbyssOrangeMix series Model.

I am using the NAI model [e6e8e1fc] to train.

Able to work with all mixed models based on NAI(i.e. AbyssOrangeMix, Anything v3, ChilloutMix)

If you like this LORA, please comment and give it a like.❤️

Any suggestions are welcome to comment here.

And also welcome to share your creations.

Enjoy it!
